# Feature Requirements

## Tab 1: Discovery Screen (`discovery_screen.dart`)

### Header Section
- App title "Discovery" in heading2 style
- Search icon button (top right)
- Category filter chips (Featured, Bushcraft, Glamping)
- Horizontal scrollable, Featured selected by default

### Camp Wiki Section
- Section title with graduation cap icon
- "View All" link
- Horizontal scrollable cards (140x180px)
- Each card shows:
  - Background image placeholder
  - Gradient overlay (bottom to top, black 80% to transparent)
  - Category badge (10px text, accent color)
  - Article title (12px, white, bold)
- On tap: Navigate to Wiki Detail Screen

### Trending Feed
- Section title "Trending Feed"
- Masonry/Grid layout (2 columns)
- Featured posts can span 2 columns
- Each post card shows:
  - Image placeholder (variable height)
  - "Plan Included" badge if applicable
  - Post title (18px, bold)
  - Creator avatar and name
  - Heart icon for likes
- On tap: Navigate to Post Detail Screen
- On avatar tap: Navigate to Creator Profile Screen

### Data Requirements
- List of WikiArticle objects
- List of Post objects
- Category filters
- Search functionality (future)

---

## Tab 2: Plan Screen (`plan_screen.dart`)

### Active Plan Card
- Prominent card with left border (4px, primary color)
- Plan title and dates
- Weather info (temperature, condition icon)
- Status badge ("Good to go", "Check weather", etc.)
- Two action buttons:
  - "Gear Check" (primary button)
  - "Share" (secondary button)
- Decorative circle element (top right)

### Packing List Section
- Section title with completion percentage
- Category filter chips (All, Sleep, Cook, etc.)
- Scrollable list of gear items
- Each item shows:
  - Icon/emoji (48x48px)
  - Item name and category
  - Condition/notes
  - Checkbox (checked/unchecked)
- Checked items have strikethrough text and lower opacity

### Import Section
- Dashed border card with accent color
- "Import from Saved Plans" CTA
- Icon indicator

### State Management
- Active plan state
- Gear items list with packed status
- Category filter state
- Completion percentage calculation

---

## Tab 3: Camp Log Screen (`camp_log_screen.dart`)

### Header
- Screen title "Camp Log"
- "Create Vlog" button (top right, accent color)

### Timeline View
- Vertical timeline with connecting line (2px, gray)
- Timeline dots (12px):
  - Primary color for most recent
  - Gray for older entries
- Each log entry shows:
  - Date/time stamp
  - Location name (optional)
  - Photo grid (1-4 photos)
  - Text content
  - Card with rounded corner cut (top left)

### Floating Action Button
- Position: bottom right, above nav bar
- Size: 56px diameter
- Color: primary color
- Icon: camera
- Shadow: float shadow
- On tap: Open camera/gallery picker

### Data Requirements
- List of LogEntry objects sorted by date
- Photo storage handling
- Location data (optional)

---

## Tab 4: Community Screen (`community_screen.dart`)

### AI Chat Header
- Title "Camp Copilot"
- Subtitle "Your 24h AI Camping Expert"
- White background with rounded bottom corners
- Subtle shadow

### Chat Interface
- Scrollable message list
- AI messages (left aligned):
  - Robot icon avatar (32px)
  - White bubble with rounded corners
  - "AI Expert Advice:" label for detailed responses
  - Numbered lists for step-by-step guides
- User messages (right aligned):
  - User avatar (32px)
  - Primary color bubble
  - White text

### Popular Circles Section
- Section title with "More >" link
- Horizontal scrollable cards (100px width)
- Each circle shows:
  - Emoji icon (40px)
  - Circle name (12px, bold)
  - Colored background (light tint)

### Input Section
- Fixed to bottom, above nav bar
- Text input field (gray background, rounded)
- Add attachment button (left)
- Send button (right, primary color)
- Placeholder: "Ask Camp Copilot..."

### State Management
- Message list
- Input text state
- Typing indicator (future)

---

## Tab 5: Profile Screen (`profile_screen.dart`)

### Hero Section
- Cover image placeholder (256px height)
- Gradient overlay (primary color 30% opacity)
- Rounded top corners for content section

### Profile Info
- Avatar (96px, overlapping cover)
- "Edit Profile" button (top right)
- User name (24px, bold)
- Bio text (12px, gray)

### Stats Grid
- 3 columns, equal width
- Each stat card shows:
  - Label (10px, gray)
  - Value (18px, bold, primary color)
  - Unit (12px, normal)
- Stats: Mileage (km), Camps (count), Gear Value ($)
- Crown icon on Gear Value card (special badge)

### Menu Items
- "My Saved Plans" with heart icon (orange background)
- "My Gear Box" with box icon (green background)
- Each item:
  - Icon circle (32px)
  - Label text (14px, bold)
  - Chevron right icon
  - White background, rounded corners
  - Tap feedback

---

## Creator Profile Screen (`creator_profile_screen.dart`)

### Header
- Full-width cover image (288px height)
- Back button (top left, with blur background)
- Gradient overlay

### Profile Section
- Large avatar (96px)
- Follow button and message button
- Creator name with verification badge
- Stats: Followers, Trips, Plans
- Bio text
- Interest tags (3-5 pills)

### Tabs
- Posts tab
- Gear Plans tab (with count)
- Underline indicator for active tab

### Gear Plans List
- Scrollable list of plan cards
- Each plan shows:
  - Season badge
  - Plan title
  - Conditions (temperature, group size, style)
  - Estimated weight
  - Gear preview icons (first 3 items + count)
  - "Save to My Plans" button (accent color)

---

## Wiki Detail Screen (`wiki_detail_screen.dart`)

### Video Hero
- Full-width video placeholder (256px height)
- Play button overlay (56px, centered)
- Video duration badge (bottom right)
- Back button (top left)
- Share and bookmark buttons (top right)

### Title Section
- Difficulty badge (Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced)
- Category tag
- Article title (24px, bold)
- Description text (14px, gray)

### Steps Section
- "Visual Guide" heading
- Vertical timeline layout
- Each step shows:
  - Step number in circle (24px, accent color for current)
  - Connecting line to next step
  - Step title (14px, bold)
  - Step description (12px, gray)
  - Optional image
  - Optional tip box (yellow background)

### Related Gear Section
- Gray background section
- "Related Gear" heading
- List of gear items with chevron (tappable)
- Each item: icon, name, description

