## Data Models Summary

### User
- id, username, displayName, bio, followers, trips, plans, tags, avatarUrl, coverUrl

### Post
- id, title, description, imageUrls, creatorId, likes, hasPlan, category, createdAt

### CampPlan
- id, title, location, startDate, endDate, temperature, weatherCondition, status, season, estimatedWeight, gearList

### GearItem
- id, name, category, emoji, description, isPacked, condition, weight

### WikiArticle
- id, title, category, difficulty, description, videoUrl, duration, steps, relatedGear

### LogEntry
- id, date, location, photos, content, mood

### ChatMessage
- id, content, isAI, timestamp, messageType

### Circle
- id, name, emoji, memberCount, category
